### Attendance Endpoints Testing
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@userToken = Bearer YOUR_USER_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
@adminToken = Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Check In to Event
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/attendance/check-in
Authorization: {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "attendanceType": "EVENT",
  "eventId": 1,
  "notes": "Excited to attend this event",
  "checkedInBy": "Self"
}

### 2. Check In to Service
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/attendance/check-in
Authorization: {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "attendanceType": "SERVICE",
  "serviceId": 1,
  "notes": "Regular Sunday service attendance"
}

### 3. Check In to Kids Service
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/attendance/check-in
Authorization: {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "attendanceType": "KIDS_SERVICE",
  "kidsServiceId": 1,
  "notes": "Volunteering at kids service"
}

### 4. Check Out from Attendance
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/attendance/check-out
Authorization: {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "attendanceId": 1,
  "notes": "Great service today",
  "checkedOutBy": "Self"
}

### 5. Get My Attendance Records
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/attendance/my-attendance
Authorization: {{userToken}}

### 6. Get My Attendance with Pagination and Sorting
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/attendance/my-attendance?page=0&size=20&sortBy=checkInTime&sortDir=desc
Authorization: {{userToken}}

### 7. Get User Attendance (Admin Only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/attendance/user/1
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### 8. Get User Attendance with Pagination (Admin Only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/attendance/user/1?page=0&size=10&sortBy=checkInTime&sortDir=asc
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### 9. Get Event Attendance
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/attendance/event/1
Authorization: {{userToken}}

### 10. Get Service Attendance
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/attendance/service/1
Authorization: {{userToken}}

### 11. Get Kids Service Attendance
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/attendance/kids-service/1
Authorization: {{userToken}}

### 12. Get Currently Checked-In Users
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/attendance/currently-checked-in
Authorization: {{userToken}}

### 13. Get Attendance Statistics
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/attendance/stats
Authorization: {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startDate": "2025-01-01T00:00:00",
  "endDate": "2025-01-31T23:59:59",
  "attendanceType": "SERVICE"
}

### 14. Get Attendance Statistics for All Types
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/attendance/stats
Authorization: {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startDate": "2025-01-01T00:00:00",
  "endDate": "2025-01-31T23:59:59"
}

### 15. Get Most Frequent Attendees (Admin Only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/attendance/frequent-attendees
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### 16. Get Most Frequent Attendees with Pagination (Admin Only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/attendance/frequent-attendees?page=0&size=10
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### 17. Bulk Check-In Users (Admin Only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/attendance/bulk-check-in
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userIds": [1, 2, 3, 4, 5],
  "attendanceType": "SERVICE",
  "serviceId": 1,
  "notes": "Bulk check-in for Sunday service",
  "checkedInBy": "Admin"
}

### 18. Update Attendance Status (Admin Only)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/attendance/1/status?status=CHECKED_OUT&notes=Manually checked out by admin
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### 19. Get Attendance by Type
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/attendance/by-type/SERVICE
Authorization: {{userToken}}

### 20. Get Attendance by Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/attendance/by-status/CHECKED_IN
Authorization: {{userToken}}

### 21. Get Attendance by Event Type
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/attendance/by-type/EVENT
Authorization: {{userToken}}

### 22. Get Attendance by Kids Service Type
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/attendance/by-type/KIDS_SERVICE
Authorization: {{userToken}}